      "raw_text": "''The Washington Water Power company has\nbeen good to the city, and I'll tell you why.\n\n\n1T con insist on having the normal flow of the\nriver down to the falls 1t has the power to prevent\nthe diversion of the water It could assert it's rights\nand yet it never has complained because the people\nof this city are using water from the river"
